UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Demetria is chief advisor to the Grand Crusader. She is called the Oracle due to her \'otherworldly\' senses. She has successfully assisted the Crusade in several of their victories against the Scourge.$B$BWhile this ruse was successful in exposing her, if she truly does possess psychic powers, she will undoubtedly be expecting some sort of trouble. You are going to provide that \'trouble.\'$B$BTrack down the Oracle and terminate her. They should be moving out of Tyr\'s Hand as we speak. Make me proud, worm.' WHERE `word_id` = 271520; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6148
