UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Get this straight, $R - we are NOT part of the Alliance!  The Wildhammers are independent, relying on deeds and actions to prove one\'s worth, rather than the blather of those who use jibber-jabber to bolster their do-nothing attitudes!$B$BIf you\'re looking for friends here, then prove your worth to us first!  The foul trolls that choke the hillsides of the Hinterlands sometimes carry tribal necklaces. Bring five of them to me, and we\'ll mark it down as a step in the right direction for you.' WHERE `word_id` = 137381; -- locales_quest - details : entry=2880
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Get yourself squared away, learn the layout of the land, and come back to me whenever you need training. I\'ll be here night or day.$B$BThe Knights of the Silver Hand have done well in making this place fairly safe, but as you meet the other citizens, I think you\'ll find they all have problems they could use some help with - help a $C can give them. Good luck.' WHERE `word_id` = 137806; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=3100
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Getting the information on Nazz is quite a favor, $N. Yes, quite a favor. But you\'ve come all the way from the Shimmering Flats to get it... are you willing to travel some more?$B$BWhile I contact my sources, why don\'t you gather something for me, eh?$B$BHm... what will it be?  How about dream dust, from the dragon whelps of the Swamp of Sorrows. Yes, I\'d love some dream dust for my snuff pouch!$B$BGet it for me, $N, and I\'ll give you the information you seek.' WHERE `word_id` = 134819; -- locales_quest - details : entry=1116
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Gifts, treats, presents... bah, I say!$B$BThose goblins pollute the true meaning of this season - the Feast of Winter Veil. This is a time of renewal; the land slumbers under a blanket of snow brought forth by Greatfather Winter, who is NOT the bumbling fool over there in the red suit!$B$BIf you\'re interested in learning what the Feast is all about for yourself, ask Historian Karnik at the Explorer\'s League. I\'m sure he\'ll be surprised that someone cares about history rather than getting presents.' WHERE `word_id` = 141811; -- locales_quest - details : entry=7062
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Gifts, treats, presents... bah, I say!$B$BThose goblins pollute the true meaning of this season - the Feast of Winter Veil. This is a time of renewal; the land slumbers under a blanket of snow brought forth by Greatfather Winter, who is NOT the bumbling fool over there in the red suit!$B$BIf you\'re interested in learning what the Feast is all about for yourself, ask Sagorne Creststrider. I\'m sure he\'ll be surprised that someone cares about history rather than getting presents.' WHERE `word_id` = 141721; -- locales_quest - details : entry=6964
