UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Revenge has a sweet taste, don\'t you think? When you destroyed the Agamands, did you catch any hint of free will within them? I hope so. I hope they knew fear before they were smashed into oblivion.$B$BIt is a foolish hope, I know. But it is a hope I foster nonetheless.' WHERE `word_id` = 131640; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=354
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Rhag Garmason wants you to locate Ol\' Rustlocke.' WHERE `word_id` = 132844; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=631
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Rhapsody Shindigger in The Hinterlands wants you to bring him 3 Roc Gizzards, 3 Groddoc Livers and 3 Ironfur Livers.' WHERE `word_id` = 135662; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=1452
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Rhapsody Shindigger! That\'s right... how could I forget such a name?$B$BSo he knew about the sinking of the temple all along? Well, that certainly would have saved you some leg work.$B$BBut this Atal\'ai artifact! Why, it\'s quite a find!' WHERE `word_id` = 135713; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=1469
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Rhapsody took quite a liking to the booze. Now don\'t get me wrong -- all of us dwarves up here at the aviary love a good ale when the time is right.$B$BBut ol\' Shindigger took to the liquor like a gryphon takes to the skies. And a damned shame it was, too. No one could fly like Rhapsody.$B$BFirst sign of trouble was when he came stumbling back from that mission with your buddy, Brohann. All went down hill quickly after that. Had to let him go.$B$BLast I heard, he\'s set up a brew camp to the east of here...' WHERE `word_id` = 135657; -- locales_quest - details : entry=1451
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Ridding Felwood of Xavathras is only the first step in a long process. It will take much work to repair the damage that has been done here.$B$BI sense that there is something much larger than just the satyrs at work here, but we will only know the truth with time...' WHERE `word_id` = 139103; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=4421
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Ride a hippogryph to Auberdine from the hippogryph master Vesprystus, then bring Nessa\'s Collection to Laird.' WHERE `word_id` = 141213; -- locales_quest - objectives : entry=6342
UPDATE `trans_words` SET `content_loc5`='Rifts stir, tear, and collapse all around us, $R. Not two paces from where I stand is a tear leading through the depths of Blackrock Mountain, into the maw of the Firelord.$B$BSurprised? Pity... The mortal races cannot comprehend that which they cannot see, touch, or feel.$B$BI assure you, the portal is there and access is possible.$B$BI\'ve piqued your interest? Attunement is simple. Venture into Blackrock Depths and retrieve a core fragment. Return it to me and I shall attune your essence with the portal.' WHERE `word_id` = 142093; -- locales_quest - details : entry=7487
